Date: 11 Jul 2006 03:42:45 -0400 (EDT)
From: A-Lan Banks <A-Lan.Banks@thomson.com>
Source: News Today Online, Iloilo City, Philippines, 10 Jul 2006, [edited]
<http://www.thenewstoday.info/2006/07/10/dengue.downs.another.4.year.old.girl.in.city.html>

Another 4-year-old girl from the barangay of Calaparan, Iloilo City died of
dengue fever late last week. The victim is the 2nd from the said barangay
to have died of the same disease, which brings the total dengue casualties
in the city to 3.
